{"tid":2487510,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 呂布軍第三十二次股東大會，MSFT獲勝，改革後靈活操作危機將降至最低，請跟隨本將軍入陣！","createTime":"2021-04-13T14:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:22:49.000Z","uid":149018,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"62cd61282f366906eb4142791878fb7764c5a107","tid":2487510,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第三十一次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdVeV61C1VfT6Yke6AP16y7XagA8pNoGbVbPP31YHMhmv?filename=kFhrHfV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFhrHfV.png&h=4fe3f28b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmde4NXEJZXy7x4PkqdPfhQS4czCXGmSBr7qNY4EXw2an2?filename=YXZ5XPf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXZ5XPf.png&h=b39317c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZFNCvcybHKHEueBT9ubB4RHyHuNHeV6XCUKX6rESjzKQ?filename=5n9EQvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5n9EQvr.png&h=e6c6380d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">688.69</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-31.13</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第三十二波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣ETF進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為陷陣營主軍短期戰線靈活操作，二軍為守軍呂布親領赤兔部隊留守主城。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團提議陷陣營進攻方向．<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領意見<br />\n2. 奉先將選取對是次行軍方向分析最精闢之意見作進軍。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計約<span class=\"red\">23:00-02:00</span>。<br />\n4. 二軍赤兔隊現正駐軍RBLX、FOXA、GME，狀態樂觀歡迎交流。<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、開市緊急調動或盤後07:45<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權，以上時機有機會皆為浮雲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYF8CYZdgnU2H7XkzghXoDmFVQLdkDD3Er92aqfVyg8g9?filename=4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第三十一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2484998/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2484998/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呂布贏回數串燒賣，武力100 智力69操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">呂布曰：奉先現已明白靈活操作之法，不局限於固定時間入陣及退兵，進可攻退可守！愛將們請獻計！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeP5pK9UwVDkwePF5RmALqQiF2TYPiJNKDXUUia6ptZYt?filename=OUBoKwR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUBoKwR.jpg&h=acd99edc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c36fc87f1f60522be6aa87da91a4a7af5de764f2","tid":2487510,"uid":374209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a2eaaf04d5bfe3b806b3fb8b455f7e298f6a4a","tid":2487510,"uid":182307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:47:48.000Z","msg":"tqqq"},{"pid":"5304c7f1e43b73ad7d9802ff1472aaae356a8fd4","tid":2487510,"uid":33674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62cd61282f366906eb4142791878fb7764c5a107","tid":2487510,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第三十一次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFhrHfV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFhrHfV.png&h=4fe3f28b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YXZ5XPf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYXZ5XPf.png&h=b39317c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5n9EQvr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5n9EQvr.png&h=e6c6380d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">688.69</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-31.13</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第三十二波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\